item.title: CVE-2015-10004|2024-08-06T08:58:24.640Z -- github.com%2Frobbert229%2Fjwt -- github.com%2Frobbert229%2Fjwt
item.description: Token validation methods are susceptible to a timing side-channel during HMAC comparison. With a large enough number of requests over a low latency connection, an attacker may use this to determine the expected HMAC.
